<author>mạykl ạ̹sḥạq, mạykl ạ̹sḥạq</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿạyzyn slạmk ymlạnạ wyfyḍ
 yạ mṣdr kl slạm
 ạmlk brwḥk jwạnạ ạsẖbʿnạ byk ṭwl ạlạ̉yạm
 ʿạyzyn nʿysẖ mʿ kl ạlnạs bmḥbẗ wwdạʿẗ wwỷạm
 yẓhr slạmk fy ḥyạtnạ fy slwknạ wf kl klạm
 ạlqrạr- ạlmjd lyk fy ạlʿly̱ wʿly̱ ạlạ̉rḍ
 ạlslạm
 wbạlnạs ạlmsrẗ yạ ạ̹lhnạ lyk kl ạlạ̹krạm
 2- ʿạyzynk ạ̹nt fy bywtnạ tạkẖd mkạnk wsṭynạ
 dy lqmẗ yạbsẗ mʿạhạ slạm ạ̉fḍl wạ̉ḥsn kdạ
 lynạ
 tʿạla kẖd wḍʿk fynạ ạ̉ydnạ wạsmk bạ̹ydynạ
 kẖly msẖwrtk wạlạ̉fkạr bslạm wḥkmẗ tqwynạ</lyrics>
<title>ʿạyzyn slạmk ymlạnạ</title>
</song>